OL,3,CWelsh MP says he was sexually abused
OL,4,Cby National Youth Theatre founder
OL,6,FWelsh Labour MP Sir Chris Bryant has
OL,7,Frevealed that he was sexually abused
OL,8,Fas a teenager by the founder of the
OL,9,FNational Youth Theatre.
OL,11,FBryant said Michael Croft, who died in
OL,12,F1986, had invited him to dinner every
OL,13,Fevening while he was attending the
OL,14,Fdrama group in London during the
OL,15,Fsummer of 1978. Bryant was 16 at the
OL,16,Ftime and Croft was 40 years older.
OL,18,FThe MP described the incident, saying
OL,19,Fwhile at Croft's house one evening he
OL,20,Fcame back from the toilet to find his
OL,21,Fhost naked except for a silk robe.
