OL,6,FHe said Croft then asked him for oral
OL,7,Fsex, and he felt no option but to go
OL,8,Fthrough with it.
OL,10,FIn an interview with The Sunday Times,
OL,11,Fthe MP for Rhondda and Ogmore said: "I
OL,12,Fdon't like telling this very much
OL,13,Fbecause I've not told it very often.
OL,15,F"It was always the same Italian in
OL,16,FKing's Cross. He would eat and drink,
OL,17,FI would eat, then he would
OL,18,Ftheoretically give me a lift home,
OL,19,Fexcept I always ended up at his house."
