OL,6,FBryant said Croft never made an
OL,7,Fadvance towards him again, with the
OL,8,Fpair remaining friends. An ordained
OL,9,Fminister, he later agreed to conduct
OL,10,FCroft's funeral.
OL,12,F"He behaved absolutely appallingly,
OL,13,Fit's despicable," said Chris Bryant.
OL,15,F"Michael, in my case, managed to spot
OL,16,Fsomebody who was gay at a time when
OL,17,Fnearly all homosexuality was illegal `
OL,18,Fcertainly very frowned on ` so
OL,19,Fpresumed that people would keep a
OL,20,Fsecret."
