OL,6,FHe said at least one other friend was
OL,7,Falso abused by Croft during his
OL,8,FNational Youth Theatre days.
OL,10,FThe 63-year-old also said he has been
OL,11,Fsexually assaulted by five male MPs
OL,12,Fduring his time in Westminster,
OL,13,Falthough he has not named or reported
OL,14,Fthem.
OL,16,F"There was no system for doing so and
OL,17,FI was frightened it would make me look
OL,18,Fbad," he said, adding he felt
OL,19,Fhomophobia in Parliament has declined
OL,20,Fduring his 24 years as an MP.
