OL,6,F"As we set out in a public statement
OL,7,Fon the case in 2017, we stand in
OL,8,Fsolidarity with all victims of abuse
OL,9,Fand encourage anyone who has
OL,10,Fexperienced abuse, no matter how long
OL,11,Fago, to speak to someone and access
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,F"In this case the perpetrator has been
OL,15,Fdeceased since 1986, but all reports
OL,16,Fmade to us will be dealt with in
OL,17,Faccordance with our robust and
OL,18,Fformalised safeguarding policy and
OL,19,Fpractice.
